rows.label: tlk70000018_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Huh? You think I'm just
sitting around fishing up
something for my dinner?

rows.label: tlk70000018_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Nah, I'm a fisherman by
trade, you see. So I'm
actually working right now.

rows.label: tlk70000018_02_msg0003
rows.name:
There's never much biting, though.
Iira's got a lot of desert, and that
means fish numbers stay pretty low.

rows.label: tlk70000018_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Since there's not much to catch,
the seafood eaten in Iira is
mostly imported or farmed...

rows.label: tlk70000018_02_msg0005
rows.name:
So, as a fisherman, it's my
passion to bring fresh,
wild-caught fish to my customers.
